## Overview

This project documents the creation of a virtualized IT help desk lab environment using VirtualBox, Windows Server 2022, and Windows 11 machines.

The lab simulates a small organizational network environment with:
- Active Directory
- Domain-joined workstations
- Static IP configuration
- User management
- Remote administration
- Help desk troubleshooting scenarios

The purpose of this project is to gain hands-on experience with common IT support and system administration tasks.

