## Explore Active Directory

- Open:
  - `server manager > tools > active directory users and computers`

- Create new user:
  - `expand domain > users`
  - `right click > new > user`

- Reset password:
  - `right click user > reset password`

- View user info in CMD:
```cmd
net user tom /domain
```

