## Set Up Windows 11 Machine

- Download Windows 11 ISO
- Create VM in VirtualBox
  - `new > (name it desktop01) > select windows 11 > finish`
  - `right click VM > settings`
    - `system > enable EFI`
    - `security > enable TPM`
    - `display > set video memory to 128 MB`
    - `configure CPU and memory`
  - `settings > network`
    - `adapter 1 > internal network > LABNET`
    - `adapter 2 > NAT`

- Start VM
  - `select downloaded Windows 11 ISO`

---

## Install Windows 11 Pro

- Select:
  - `windows 11 pro`

- Choose:
  - `I don't have a product key`

- At network screen:
  - `Shift + F10`

- Type:
```cmd
OOBE\BYPASSNRO
```

- Press Enter
- Wait for reboot

- Select:
  - `I don't have internet`
  - `continue with limited setup`

- Create local admin account:
  - `labadmin`

