## Enable Ping Through Windows Firewall on Windows 11 Machines

- Perform steps on:
  - `desktop01`
  - `desktop02`

- Open Windows Firewall:
  - `Windows + R > wf.msc`

- Navigate:
  - `Inbound Rules`

- Locate:
  - `File and Printer Sharing (Echo Request - ICMPv4-In)`

- Enable:
  - `Private`
  - `Domain`

- Right click each rule:
  - `Enable Rule`

- Verify network profile:
  - `Settings > Network & Internet > Ethernet`
  - `ensure internal adapter is set to Private`

