## Onboard desktop01 Machine onto Domain

- Open:
  - `this pc > properties`
  - `system > about`

- Navigate to:
  - `Domain or Workgroup`

- Change to domain:
  - `woodtech`

- Restart machine

- Users created in Active Directory can now log into:
  - `desktop01`

- RDP can also be enabled to remotely connect to:
  - `CA-DC-01`

